{"tid":2044684,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"毋忘初心 612一週年","createTime":"2020-05-31T09:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T19:34:48.000Z","uid":304230,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d41b8ac2ead6aa12eb154eebd164e20175636ce2","tid":2044684,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXAjdhc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXAjdhc.jpg&h=6f8b2b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97KzMCh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97KzMCh.jpg&h=f81df50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zGjHa33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzGjHa33.jpg&h=212df1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就黎612一週年啦 ！<br />\n希望大家拎住呢隻杯！<br />\n毋忘初心！<br />\n一日未贏 一日都唔會放棄！<br />\n<br />\n而612亦開始告急!<br />\n我地會扣除成本全數捐出！<br />\n售價為$100 ！<br />\n每款限量500隻！<br />\n將於3/6發售 敬請留意！<br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝 @arkisan.hk <br />\n好有心機幫我地設計 <br />\n每幅圖都有佢特別意義 <br />\n改圖改左成個月<br />\n多謝你唔會厭棄我咁麻煩<br />\n而圖中有幾個特別含意 <br />\n唔知你地又搵唔搵到呢？<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以留意住我地ig<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/teaonlyhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fteaonlyhk%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdKZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=6bc2a0e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/teaonlyhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命</span></span>[/quote]"},{"pid":"3656f4e0fcb8a3226f0a8ee22a660f4b1bca4f66","tid":2044684,"uid":107717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"幾多ml？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攞嚟買茶會唔會裝唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbetween樓豬好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3817824d259d23b1785c146e